title: Crime Invasion: Britain's New Underworld With Rageh Omaar s01
description:
Crime Invasion is a documentary series, hosted by Rageh Omaar, which takes a look at the new wave of criminal masterminds invading Great Britain.

In this episode Rageh Omaar meets the Met&#039;s Stolen Vehicles Unit and tells the story of Operation Aberdale, in which ten people, including a former DVLA official and trainee police officer, were jailed for their roles in one of the UK&#039;s most prolific car-ringing gangs.
